divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband and I saw from our balcony facing east a very bright, round pulsing object, colors fluctuating, slowly moving across the sky until behind tree line. I have 20 minutes of video. We noticed it because it was brighter than anything in the sky with exception to the moon.
